  "questionNumber": "070-0333",
  "stemHtml": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(74,74,105);\">Who shall the operator make a report to if there is a malfunction of an aircraft that has or may have endangered its safe operation but that has not resulted in an accident or serious incident?</span></p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>To the competent authority and to the organisation responsible for the design of the aircraft. </p>",
    "b": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(74,74,105);\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:13.0509px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">To the competent authority and to any other organisation required to be informed by the State of the operator.  </span></span></p>",
    "c": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(74,74,105);\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:13.0509px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">To EASA and to the organisation responsible for the design of the aircraft.  </span></span></p>",
    "d": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(74,74,105);\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;display:inline !important;float:none;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:13.0509px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">To EASA and to any other organisation required to be informed by the State of the operator.</span></span></p>"
  },
  "correctOption": "a",
